Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 姆伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 姆伽罗就是姆伽罗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿萨谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想救恶魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从斗技场逃跑的几人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今仍在逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防他们逃离王都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已布下严密的包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助逃跑的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是法瓦罗·雷欧涅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会一并解决掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我们一定会解决它的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有他们的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙也出现过数次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要追下去想必早晚能遇上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发现 就地杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么放跑他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在竟然还出这么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今失去艾尔意昧着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻动身搜查艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要把艾尔带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他如果被人类抓住 会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能眼睁睁看着他去死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算去了 也只是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 既然艾尔不信任你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你们去了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有一人我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会以为这样就算乔装了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿萨谢尔去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 早上人就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不会炸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道？你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着啊 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是师傅 无敌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 看来你也一样啊 唯独狗屎运过人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这表情啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…你看我就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥见到凯撒就脸红了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很久没像这样闹过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好想喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少年是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在神界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凯撒·利德法尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原先是你妈妈的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才多久没见 就变拽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想查清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯王接下来打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王在先前的战斗中使用的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那破坏力太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要王有意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与十年前相当的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会再度降临在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让人类走回正道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的力量能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 你个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 只要能封印那个兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论王的意图是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能阻止破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手镯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？手镯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见王驱动那个黑球时的场景了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个手镯有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢走那个手镯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗 你要是违背我们的约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先搜集情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果夏利欧斯正在酝酿巨大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我们来阻止他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我跟着还出了这种事 真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他跑了是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草率解放了他的力量也是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们太性急了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被艾尔的力量冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果忘了他的精神还不足以驾驭这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想失去恩人艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我衷心希望 能立刻将他从人间带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让他一直陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 搜查的任务就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你一定会救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去人间找艾尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们母子救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次该你为我们母子贡献力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人间 你是被通缉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切记不要轻易做出危险的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能发誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这下我就跟巴卡斯一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟真的恶魔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去搜集情报咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜小姐兴奋地冲出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙无忧无虑的 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是跟去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓？为啥要我去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是她师傅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有毛关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 爆炸头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得小妹妹会被卷入什么纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了 法瓦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是谁的墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母亲的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这么吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才没吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为平民却成了王的侧室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚怀上我就被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就只是个悲哀的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上的皇室血脉 曾是她活着的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便生活贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她依然梦想着 王室早晚会来接她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果这个梦没能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特的烈火轻而易举地要了她的命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲也被巴哈姆特的火球…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因巴哈姆特一事 我被纳入了王室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字从妈妈取的克里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了夏利欧斯17世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是住在贫民街的恶魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想去趟贫民街了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 能带个路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带路？好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他刚才说我是恶魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雕刻有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这样不就暴露长相了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去下个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把头巾都取了 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不妥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我有很多问题想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看左上方墙上的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在监视你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甩掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算甩掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个手镯有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身为国王 干了很多招神 招恶魔讨厌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 化身为克里斯的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却对我很温柔 还跟我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能笑着面对恶魔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道哪张脸才是真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论付出多少代价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去完成某些事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什么 我目前无法回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我的所作所为都是为了实现目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为国王 我做出了抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就是现在这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已抛弃所谓的罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了质问自己的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了愚蠢母亲的墓前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止 这份信念从未动摇过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我唯独割舍不下你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是你出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便能想往常一样 以王的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是遇见了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何想当个可怕的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想分担你背负的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以随时随地变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为接吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面要到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次是多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多久 多久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就是下次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果还有机会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会说出我的目标的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然早就被红龙迷惑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是亚纳提的凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天界的贞德 你那边怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 这里是天界的贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超闪耀 超耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不言败
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 请详细解说下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说很耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周也要看哦
